graph LR
    KServe[KServe Operator<br/>Controller + Webhook]

    %% External Dependencies (Required/Optional)
    KServe -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.24+<br/>Required]
    KServe -->|serverless mode| Knative[Knative Serving 1.8+<br/>Optional]
    KServe -->|traffic mgmt| Istio[Istio 1.16+<br/>Optional]
    KServe -->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager 1.10+<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    KServe -->|traffic policies| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Istio<br/>VirtualService CRs]
    KServe -.->|model metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>gRPC/9090]

    %% External Storage Services
    KServe -->|model storage| S3[S3 Storage<br/>AWS/MinIO/Ceph<br/>HTTPS/443]
    KServe -->|model storage| GCS[GCS Storage<br/>Google Cloud<br/>HTTPS/443]
    KServe -->|model storage| Azure[Azure Blob Storage<br/>HTTPS/443]

    %% Integration Points - ODH Components
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management| KServe
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|auto deployment| KServe
    Workbench[Data Science Workbench] -.->|model training| KServe

    %% Monitoring and Observability
    KServe -->|metrics export| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>HTTP/8080]
    KServe -.->|distributed tracing| OpenTelemetry[OpenTelemetry<br/>Optional]

    %% Downstream consumers
    KServe -->|inference API| Applications[Applications<br/>REST/gRPC clients]

